name: RedmondGuide
0:
”alexa, open redmond guide”
”tell me about Redmond”
”tell me top five things to do”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: redmond guide
des: The skill will allow for a user to ask for the top 5 things that are popular to do and top 5 places that are popular attractions. First off, the top 5 things that are popular will explain certain attractions and how they are interesting. This could mean that someone could site see in the location or just play a small game of golf. The 5 places would explain areas that draw attention to tourists and are often a very spectacular visit!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
